    Closed --> [*]

    note right of Unconnected
        Socket created without connection.
        Must call connect() before getInputStream()/getOutputStream().
        bind() can be called to set local address.
        setReceiveBufferSize() should be called before connect() for large windows.
    end note

    note right of ConnectedInputShutdown
        Input half closed: getInputStream() not available.
        Output stream still operational.
    end note

    note right of ConnectedOutputShutdown
        Output half closed: getOutputStream() not available.
        Input stream still operational.
    end note

    note right of ConnectedBothShutdown
        Both halves shut down.
        Neither getInputStream() nor getOutputStream() available.
    end note

    note right of Closed
        Terminal state. Socket cannot be reconnected or rebound.
        isConnected() and isBound() remain true if they were true before close().
    end note
